          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Perkins Loan Program Inflation Adjustment Act of 2016</b></p> <p>This bill amends title IV (Student Assistance) of the Higher Education Act of 1965 to adjust the maximum annual and aggregate amount that a student may borrow under the Federal Perkins Loan program to account for inflation. </p>]]></text>
